#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:22
#, no-c-format
msgid "Technical References"
msgstr "Documentazione tecnica"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:24
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&ktuberling; offers a gentle and rewarding introduction to &kde; "
"customization and programming. The application can be extended. For example, "
"without any coding, new playgrounds can be added by changing the graphics "
"files. By adding appropriate sound files, translators can change the sounds "
"to their native tongue!"
msgstr ""
"&ktuberling; fornisce un'introduzione agevole e gratificante alla "
"programmazione e personalizzazione in &kde;. Questa applicazione può essere "
"estesa. Per esempio, si possono introdurre nuove scene cambiando i file "
"grafici, senza bisogno di programmare. Aggiungendo gli appropriati file "
"sonori, i traduttori possono mettere i commenti sonori nella propria lingua."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:32
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you extend or add to the game please consider sending your additions to "
"the maintainer <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex Fiestas</ulink> for "
"inclusion in future releases."
msgstr ""
"Se crei estensioni o aggiunte al gioco, considera l'idea di inviare i tuoi "
"contributi allo sviluppatore <ulink url=\"mailto:alex@eyeos.org\">Alex "
"Fiestas</ulink> affinché possa includerli nelle prossime versioni."

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:39
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Artists"
msgstr "Per i disegnatori"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:41
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; playground you have to:"
msgstr "Per creare una nuova scena di &ktuberling; devi:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:47
#, no-c-format
msgid "Draw the playground in a &SVG; file, there you have to:"
msgstr "Disegnare lo sfondo in formato &SVG;, per farlo dovrai:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:49
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name the place where items can dragged <quote>background</quote>."
msgstr ""
"Dare un nome al punto dove gli oggetti possono essere trascinati sullo "
"<quote>sfondo</quote>."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:50
#, no-c-format
msgid "Name each of the draggable items with an unique name."
msgstr "Dare un nome univoco a tutti gli oggetti trascinabili."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:56
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal> file, it has to follow "
"this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Creare un file <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>. Che deve "
"rispettare questo schema:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:57
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;object name=\"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" scale=\"<replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/playground&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;playground gameboard=\"<replaceable>TuoFileSVG</replaceable>\" name="
"\"<replaceable>IlFileDesktop</replaceable>\"&gt;\n"
"    &lt;object name=\"<replaceable>NomeOggetto</replaceable>\" sound="
"\"<replaceable>NomeSuono</replaceable>\" scale="
"\"<replaceable>ValoreOpportuno</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"    ...\n"
"    ...\n"
"    ...\n"
"    &lt;/playground&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:59
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourSVGFile</replaceable> is the name of the &SVG; file that "
"has the drawing."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>TuoFileSVG</replaceable> è il nome del file &SVG; che contiene "
"il disegno."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:60
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>theDesktopFile</replaceable> is the name of the desktop file "
"that has the name of the theme."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>IlFileDesktop</replaceable> è il nome del file del desktop che "
"ha il nome del tema."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:62
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each object you need a <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>itemName</replaceable> is the unique name you used on the &SVG; "
"file, <replaceable>soundName</replaceable> is the sound name that will be "
"played when dragging it, see the <filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</"
"filename> file from source code for more information."
msgstr ""
"Per ogni oggetto ti serve una voce <literal>&lt;object&gt;</literal>. "
"<replaceable>NomeOggetto</replaceable> è il nome univoco che hai usato nel "
"file &SVG;, <replaceable>NomeSuono</replaceable> è la voce che si sente "
"quando trascini l'oggetto. Vedi il file <filename>sounds/soundthemes.HOWTO</"
"filename> presente nel codice sorgente per maggiori informazioni."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:66
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<literal>scale</literal> is optional and <replaceable>someValue</"
"replaceable> is the scale factor that will be used when drawing this object "
"outside the warehouse, if not specified is 1."
msgstr ""
"<literal>scale</literal> è opzionale e <replaceable>ValoreOpportuno</"
"replaceable> è il fattore di scala che viene applicato all'oggetto quando "
"viene trascinato fuori dal deposito. Se non è specificato, sarà 1."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:72
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> file, it has to "
"follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Per creare un file <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> bisogna "
"seguire questo schema:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:73
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"[KTuberlingTheme]\n"
"Name=<replaceable>themeName</replaceable>"
msgstr ""
"[KTuberlingTheme]\n"
"Name=<replaceable>NomeTema</replaceable>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:75
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>themeName</replaceable> is the name that identifies the theme, "
"will be shown in the Playground menu."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>NomeTema</replaceable> è il nome che identifica il tema. Verrà "
"mostrato nel menu Scena."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:81
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the theme to &ktuberling; repository, add <literal role="
"\"extension\">.svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, "
"and <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files to <literal>FILES</"
"literal> section of the <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> into the "
"<filename class=\"directory\">pics/</filename> folder."
msgstr ""
"Se vuoi aggiungere il tuo tema nel deposito di &ktuberling;, devi aggiungere "
"i file <literal role=\"extension\">.svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension"
"\">.theme</literal> e <literal role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> alla "
"sezione <literal>FILES</literal> del file <filename>CMakeLists.txt</"
"filename> nella cartella <filename class=\"directory\">pics/</filename>."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:89
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you want to install it for yourself, place <literal role=\"extension\">."
"svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal>, and <literal "
"role=\"extension\">.desktop</literal> files into the <filename class="
"\"directory\">ktuberling/pics</filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Se vuoi installarlo per te stesso, copia i file <literal role=\"extension\">."
"svg</literal>, <literal role=\"extension\">.theme</literal> e <literal role="
"\"extension\">.desktop</literal> all'interno della cartella <filename class="
"\"directory\">ktuberling/pics</filename> in <userinput><command>qtpaths</"
"command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: title
#: technical-reference.docbook:100
#, no-c-format
msgid "For Translators"
msgstr "Per i traduttori"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:102
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Besides the usual <literal role=\"extension\">.po</literal> files mechanism "
"for translating program labels and prompts, the sounds can be localized too."
msgstr ""
"Oltre all'abituale sistema dei file <literal role=\"extension\">.po</"
"literal> per tradurre messaggi e richieste del programma, occorrerà "
"localizzare anche i file sonori."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:107
#, no-c-format
msgid "To create a new &ktuberling; sound theme you have to:"
msgstr "Per creare un nuovo tema sonoro per &ktuberling; devi:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:112
#, no-c-format
msgid "Record the sounds in OGG Vorbis rc3 file format."
msgstr "Registrare i suoni su file con formato OGG Vorbis rc3."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:113
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Create a <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file, it has to follow this schema:"
msgstr ""
"Creare un file <filename><replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</"
"replaceable></filename>. soundtheme file, che deve avere questo schema:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:115
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>"
"\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<replaceable>relativePath</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/language&gt;"
msgstr ""
"&lt;language code=\"<replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</replaceable>"
"\"&gt;\n"
"&lt;sound name=\"<replaceable>NomeSuono</replaceable>\" file="
"\"<replaceable>PercorsoRelativo</replaceable>\" /&gt;\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"...\n"
"&lt;/language&gt;"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:117
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> is your language two "
"letter code, for example gl for Galician."
msgstr ""
"<replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</replaceable> è il codice in due "
"lettere che individua la tua lingua, ad esempio \"it\" per italiano."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:119
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"For each sound a <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal> entry. "
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable> should match with the soundName "
"specified in the playground theme (see the <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</"
"filename> from source code). <replaceable>relativePath</replaceable> should "
"be the relative path you are going to install the file with this sound to, "
"typically it will be <filename><replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>soundName</replaceable>.<replaceable>format</replaceable></"
"filename> (<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable> can be your language "
"two letter code for example)."
msgstr ""
"Per ogni suono serve una riga <literal>&lt;sound&gt;</literal>. "
"<replaceable>NomeSuono</replaceable> deve corrispondere al NomeSuono "
"specificato nel tema della scena (vedi <filename>pics/themes.HOWTO</"
"filename> dal codice sorgente). <replaceable>PercorsoRelativo</replaceable> "
"deve essere il percorso relativo da seguire per trovare dove è installato il "
"file con questo suono. Tipicamente sarà "
"<filename><replaceable>QualcosaDiUnivoco</replaceable>/"
"<replaceable>NomeSuono</replaceable>.<replaceable>formato</replaceable></"
"filename> (ad esempio, <replaceable>QualcosaDiUnivoco</replaceable> potrebbe "
"essere il codice di due lettere della tua lingua)."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:128
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you are adding the sound theme to &ktuberling; in your language folder:"
msgstr "Se vuoi aggiungere il tuo tema sonoro a &ktuberling;:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:130
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Add the sound files and the <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</"
"literal> files into the <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/"
"ktuberling</filename> folder of your language translations."
msgstr ""
"Aggiungi i file audio e i file <literal role=\"extension\">.soundtheme</"
"literal> nella cartella <filename class=\"directory\">data/kdegames/"
"ktuberling</filename> delle traduzioni della tua lingua."

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:133
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"On that very same dir you need a <filename>CMakeLists.txt</filename> file "
"describing how to install the files, typically it will be."
msgstr ""
"Proprio in questa cartella dovrai creare un file <filename>CMakeLists.txt</"
"filename> che indica come installare i file. La sua forma tipica è:"

#. Tag: programlisting
#: technical-reference.docbook:136
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"FILE( GLOB oggfiles *.ogg )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES ${oggfiles} DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable> )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES <replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/sounds/ )"
msgstr ""
"FILE( GLOB oggfiles *.ogg )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES ${oggfiles} DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</replaceable> )\n"
"INSTALL( FILES <replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</replaceable>."
"soundtheme DESTINATION ${KDE_INSTALL_DATADIR}/ktuberling/sounds/ )"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:141
#, no-c-format
msgid "If you want to install it for yourself:"
msgstr "Se vuoi installarlo per te stesso:"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:143
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place <filename><replaceable>yourLanguageTwoLetterCode</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> file into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds</filename> folder in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--"
"paths GenericDataLocation</option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Copia il file <filename><replaceable>Codice2LettereXTuaLingua</replaceable>."
"soundtheme</filename> nella cartella <filename class=\"directory"
"\">ktuberling/sounds</filename> in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> "
"<option>--paths GenericDataLocation </option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:146
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Place your sound files into the <filename class=\"directory\">ktuberling/"
"sounds/<replaceable>someUniquePath</replaceable></filename> folder in "
"<userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation</"
"option></userinput>"
msgstr ""
"Copia i tuoi file audio nella cartella <filename class=\"directory"
"\">ktuberling/sounds/<replaceable>unPercorsoUnivoco</replaceable></filename> "
"in <userinput><command>qtpaths</command> <option>--paths GenericDataLocation "
"</option></userinput>"

#. Tag: para
#: technical-reference.docbook:153
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Information on how to work with the translation mechanisms in &kde; is "
"available in <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/translation-howto/index."
"html\">The &kde; Translation HOWTO</ulink>."
msgstr ""
"Le informazioni su come utilizzare i meccanismi di traduzione per &kde; sono "
"disponibili su <ulink url=\"https://l10n.kde.org/docs/translation-howto/"
"index.html\">The &kde; Translation HOWTO</ulink>."

